## 🗃️ هيكل Firebase Database

```
/users/{uid}
  - uid, name, email, bio, photoURL, role

/rooms/{roomId}
  - roomId, name, ownerId, type, isLocked, password
  - /users/{uid}
  - /speakers/{uid}
  - /moderators/{uid}

/roomMessages/{roomId}/{msgId}
  - from, name, text, timestamp

/messages/{chatId}/{msgId}
  - from, text, timestamp

/userChats/{uid}/{partnerUid}
  - partnerName, lastMessage, timestamp

/friends/{uid}/{friendUid}
  - status (accepted/sent)

/friendRequests/{uid}/{senderUid}
  - senderName, status, timestamp
```

